Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「當我們嘲笑魔鬼 告訴自己它不存在時…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那就是它最開心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}-加布裏爾阿莫斯神父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}梵蒂岡首席驅魔師 1986-2016
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1987年6月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}特羅佩亞 - 意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的豬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That's a beautiful pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是最好的 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Only the best, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊請 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This way, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這男孩表現出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The boy is showing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所有典型附身跡象 阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}all the classical signs of possession, Father Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,家屬有沒有咨詢醫生？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Has the family consulted a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常多的醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Many, many doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼樣的附身跡象？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What are the signs of possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他用英語交談 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He converses in English, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他以前說過英語嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Has he spoken English before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 從來都沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Never. Not once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他們有電視機嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do they own a television?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 應該有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在畫什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一隻鳥\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That's good, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個重要任務給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have a very important job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你會念主禱文嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do you know the Our Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,會 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes, Father. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以幫你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You can help your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷重複念主禱文\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Repeat the Our Father, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不要分心 不停地念 明白嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Don't get distracted. Relentless. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在天上的父 願人都尊你的名為聖…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Our Father, who art in heaven, hallowed be thy name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把豬帶過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Bring me the pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是軍團\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是撒旦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是說骯話的龐然大物\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am foul-mouthed behemoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很難相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Difficult to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你懷疑我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You doubt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是撒旦 我叫什麼名字？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you are Satan, what is my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,形容地獄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Describe hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快會知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You will find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你在逃避我的問題嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Are you avoiding my questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你嘲笑我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我 撒旦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Answer me, Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為何附身在這男孩身上？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why possess this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為何不是更有影響力的人？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why not someone more influential?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以附身…在我選擇的任何人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I can possess anyone I choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你能附身到吉安尼神父身上嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Could you possess Father Gianni?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一個主教？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人 任何東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Anyone! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I do not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你連這隻豬都能附身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I don't believe you could even possess this pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你能嗎？你有能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Can you do it? You have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你能附身在這隻豬身上嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Could you possess the pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-是 我能 -快 撒旦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes, I can. - Come on, Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-你看好  -附身在豬身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Watch me! -Possess the pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我見識你就是黑暗王子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Show me you are the Prince of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我見識你的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Show to me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你附身了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Have you done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你附在它身上了 撒旦？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Have you possessed him, Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你附在它身上了 撒旦？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Have you possessed it, Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Be calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God blesses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你能睡了 孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You can sleep now, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,惡魔走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The demon has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝與你同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}教廷第一驅魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1987年7月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}卡斯蒂利亞 - 西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 我們不在美國了 你不能那樣穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, we're not in America anymore. You can't dress like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因為到處都會有建築工人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Because there's gonna be construction workers everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你在後面還好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How you doing back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…我們因為這個而拋棄一切？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So we left everything for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 拜託 別開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, please. Don't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 因為你就知道我打算說什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You know exactly what I'm gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 而且我不想聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, and I don't wanna hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢？還蠻酷的吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What do you think? Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咕咕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cuckoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得聖邁克爾有機會時\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why do you think Saint Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,卻沒有殺死撒旦是什麼原因？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}didn't kill Satan when he had the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一個神學的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That is a question of theology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也許正是他的憐憫留下了聖邁克爾的劍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Perhaps it was his mercy that stayed Saint Michael's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阻擋上帝之愛的唯一東西…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The only thing that arrests God's love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一個人的自由意識\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}is a person's freedom to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝連那可憎之物也給與自由…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But God cannot be God unless he allows for this choice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不然上帝就不是上帝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}even for the damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,聖邁克爾 他知道這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Saint Michael, he knows this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都將被審判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We will all be judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都將按照愛的程度…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We will all be judged
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,來面對審判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}by how much we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do not worry, Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會捍衛你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will defend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,捍衛我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Defend me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的信仰…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My faith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要捍衛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}does not require defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大家覺得如何？-舒適\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- What do you think, guys? - Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 給它一個機會 這很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, come on. Give it a chance. This is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,卡洛斯 嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Señora Vasquez. - Carlos, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能和你見面還真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So nice to put a face to the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯基貝爾神父…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Padre-- Father Esquibel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興認識你 瓦斯克斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Pleasure to meet you, Miss Vasquez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫我茱莉亞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Uh, Julia, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-卡洛斯正帶我參觀 -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Carlos was giving me a tour. -  Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想過來看看跟你和家人打個招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I just wanted to stop by and welcome you and your family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-歡迎你們來到教區 -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to the diocese. -  I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 請 請繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, no, no, no, please. Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你能平安來到真的太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm glad to see you made it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去找你的房間 笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}All right. Go find your room, twerp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 能給我一個嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hey. Can I get one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這房子年久失修\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This property has been in disrepair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-從我記事起就這樣 -謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- for as long as I can remember. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你正在做一件很棒的事 修復修道院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So it's a wonderful thing you're doing, restoring the abbey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們非常尊重現有的架構\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We are being very respectful of the existing architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它實際上已在我丈夫家中世代相傳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This has actually been in my husband's family for generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而我們剛剛繼承它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and we just inherited it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦斯克斯先生在這還是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Is Mr. Vasquez here or--?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其實他已經去世了 大約一年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, uh, he passed, actually. About a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遺憾 -沒關係\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- I'm sorry for your loss. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什麼需要 請說？不要猶豫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you need anything, please, hm, don't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我會為他祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will remember him in my prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你太好了 謝謝 很高興認識你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, that's very kind of you. Thank you. It was nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好 卡洛斯 跟我說 怎麼樣？我們在哪裏？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay, Carlos, talk to me. What's up? Where are we at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要開挖地下室十分複雜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The basement excavation is very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-比你想的更貴…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}More expensive, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-應該是 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}-  I'm afraid so. -  All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我會再看一下圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'll take another look at the plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能帶我去看看地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you could just show me what the basement looks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我能接一些…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}maybe I can wire--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 在你摔斷脖子之前快下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, get off of there before you break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是煙嗎？請馬上把它滅了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Is that a cigarette? Put that out right now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-好 -不 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Fine. - No! Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出我的房間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Get out of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到弟弟了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hey, have you seen your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看…我真的受不了我兩個孩子的沉默對待\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Look, I really can't handle the silent treatment from both my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道你不想來這裏 -確實是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- I know you don't wanna be here. - Yeah, no shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 我需要你的幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Please, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這修道院是你父親留給我們的唯一東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This abbey is the only thing your dad left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們已經沒有收入了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We don't have an income anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們把它修好後賣了就回家好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Once we fix it up and sell it, we'll go home. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你至少能幫我看好你弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Maybe if you could just at least watch your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也許嘗試讓他再次說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Maybe try and get him to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？他已經快一年沒說話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How? He hasn't spoken in almost a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你能幫我試試看嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Can you try for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我為了你做個媽媽？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So you want me to be a mother for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,請幫忙看著你的弟弟 好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Please just keep an eye on your brother. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1987年7月2日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}羅馬 - 意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Father Amorth, caffe latte?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個時候？你瘋了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}At this time of the day? Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,雙份濃縮咖啡 修女\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Double espresso, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,糖？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,糖是魔鬼的傑作 不要 謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Sugar is the work of the devil. No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繼續吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Let's get on with this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是正式聽證會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is a formal hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,按照約定 訴訟將以英語進行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And as agreed, proceedings will be undertaken in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 開始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Ah. All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,6月4日晚上 在特羅佩亞鎮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}On the night of June 4th, in the town of Tropea,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你進行了驅魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}you performed an exorcism
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,未經雷焦卡拉布裏亞主教的批准\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}without the approval of the Reggio Calabria bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,用英語 阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In English, Father Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是驅魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That was not an exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,根據吉安尼神父的描述 在雷焦卡拉布裏亞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}From Father Gianni's description, what occurred in Reggio Calabria sounded
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,發生的事就是一場驅魔 而且還有動物祭祀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}exactly like an exorcism, complete with animal sacrifice, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那男孩心理失調 是一種暫時性精神疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The boy was maladjusted. A temporary mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我用了遠古心理學\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I use primitive psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,暗示的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The power of suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個對象稱為撒旦 要求它展示它的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You addressed the subject as Satan, called for him to display his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你否認這一點嗎？-不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Do you deny this? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就是這麼做的 -你為什麼要那樣做？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- That's what I did. - And why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,驅魔是我的職責\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Exorcism is my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我被分配到的絕大多數案件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}but the vast majority of the cases to which I'm assigned
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要驅魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}do not require an exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只需要一些交談\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They just need, uh, a little conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一點同理心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}a little understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有時…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一些戲劇性\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}a little theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沙利文大主教 在我看來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cardinal Sullivan, in my observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,98% 分派給阿莫斯神父的案件…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}98% of the cases that are assigned to Father Amorth
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,過後都被他進一步推薦給\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}are then further recommended by him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,醫生和精神科醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to doctors and psychiatrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,另外2%呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And the other 2%?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,另外的2%\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Ah, the other 2%.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是長久以來 讓科學和醫學界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is something that has confounded all of science
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都感到困惑的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and all of medicine for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我稱之…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,邪惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,主教大人 成功驅魔數百次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your Eminence, with hundreds of successful exorcisms,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-阿莫斯神父一直有效率地… -稍等 盧蒙巴主教\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Father Amorth has been very effective-- - One moment, Bishop Lumumba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你確實提出了一個有意思的觀點 阿莫斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You do raise an interesting point, Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是醫生 但你的這些做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You are not a doctor, but these practices of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可能會對這些人造成破壞性影響\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}could have damaging effects on these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是心理醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am not a psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是神學家 律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But I am a theologian, I am a lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,記者 一個務實的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am a journalist, and I am a practical man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是戰爭中的游擊隊 我懂得分辨行刑隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I was also a partisan in the war, so I know a firing squad when I see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 這是怎麼回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,信理部已向\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Congregation for the Doctrine of the Faith
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,委員會推薦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}has recommended to this panel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,取消首席驅魔師一職\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}that the position of chief exorcist be formally vacated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你的意思是邪惡不存在？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So, what you are saying is that evil does not exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,教會一直面臨著提升其重要性的壓力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Church is under constant pressure to sharpen her relevance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候擺脫這些過時的信念了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's time we move past these outdated beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請向我解釋一下 主教大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Explain to me please, Your Eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不存在邪惡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If evil does not exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼教會的作用是什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}what, then, is the role of the Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為我們都要小心信理部\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I think we all have to be careful of the Congregation of the Doctrine of the Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看來 他們希望我們都失業\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Sounds to me like they want us all out of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有更多問題要問你 阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We have more questions for you, Father Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然我就值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How is it that I am suddenly worthy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些有權勢的人花時間和精神了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}of the time and attention of all you powerful men?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我再問你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I ask you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼一回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,正當程序 神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Due process, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 這與死去的女孩羅莎莉亞維倫德茲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So this is not about the dead girl, Rosaria Velendez,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我在 《上帝之母》雜誌上寫的無關？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}that I write about in La Madre di Dio magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您對此的盡職調查和流程是怎樣的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What is your due diligence and process on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-拜託 大主教 -我警告你 阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Please, cardinal. - I warn you! I warn you! Father Amorth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,尊重你的上級\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}show respect to your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是梵蒂岡的首席驅魔師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am the chief exorcist of the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的職位是由我的主教任命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My position was appointed by my bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的教區是羅馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My diocese is Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我當地的主教是教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My local bishop is the pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你對我有問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you have a problem with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以和我老闆談談 知道嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}you talk to my boss. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇的身體虛弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The pope is infirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯神父 你還不能離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Father Amorth, you have not been dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-咕咕 -阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Cuckoo. - Father Amorth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你好？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我想盡快完成這項工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I can't wait to finish this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這地方讓我很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This place freaks me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 什麼都看不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I don't know. Can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他們發現了一個天然氣礦床\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They hit a gas deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能繼續在這工作 我會讓我的團隊撤退\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We can't continue working here. I'm pulling my team from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 我們走吧 來吧 大家都出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Come on, let's go. Come on, everybody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Quick, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No. Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 亨利 發生什麼事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, my God! Henry! What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我進來時他就這樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I don't know, he was like this when I came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？亨利 是媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry? Henry, it's Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-亨利 -天啊 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Henry. - Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他在說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利 -媽媽…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Henry. - Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都會死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You're all going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利 你在做什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利 亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Henry! Henry! -  Henry! Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,X光 驗血 連脊柱穿刺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}X-rays, blood tests, even the spinal tap
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和核磁共振成像 也未顯示缺血或血腫的結果\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and MRI show no results of ischemia or hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他的所有生命體征和腦功能似乎都正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}All of his vitals and brain functions seem to be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,正常？什麼意思？他在抽搐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wait, normal? What do you mean? He was convulsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他最近受過什麼創傷嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Has he been through any trauma recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是 他爸爸在一年前過世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yeah, uh, his dad died about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他的反應如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And how did he react?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,從那以後他就沒說過話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He hasn't spoken since.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,精神病？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wha-- Psychosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不可能 他不過是個小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No, that's not possible. He's just a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 現在我們已無能為力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Ma'am, there is nothing that we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-但他能推薦一位優秀的精神科醫生 -這是什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- But he can recommend a good psychiatrist. -  What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你兒子繼續試圖傷害自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If your son continues trying to hurt himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-你可以給他這種鎮靜劑 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- you can administer him this sedative. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-媽媽 -我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Mom. - I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:23:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我覺得你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No, I don't think you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是緊急情況 拜託了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But this is an emergency, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我需要和領事館裏能幫我的人談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No, I need to talk to someone at the consulate who can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一個專家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I need a specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 拜託\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.49,0:24:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愛 過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My love, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.47,0:25:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Fuck this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.44,0:25:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Henry, no. -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.19,0:25:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利 停\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的寶貝餓了 你這肥牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This baby's hungry, you fat cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.57,0:25:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？你說什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.48,0:25:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你從來都沒有以母乳餵過我 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You never breastfed me, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.57,0:25:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼？ -搞什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- What? -  What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}恨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What the fuck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.29,0:25:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把牧師給我帶來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Bring me the priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.21,0:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-你能幫我們嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}-  Can you help us? -  Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.04,0:25:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來幫忙的 茱莉亞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm here to help, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.59,0:25:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.98,0:26:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個牧師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wrong fucking priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.54,0:26:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎 加布裏爾？-是的 教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Is that you, Gabriele? -  Yes, Holy Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.04,0:26:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他們告訴我你病了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They tell me you are sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.34,0:26:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對 他們希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, they hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.47,0:26:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他們希望看到我虛弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They wish to see me weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But, no, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Help me. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.66,0:27:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我們太盡責了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Perhaps we've done our jobs too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.29,0:27:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇利文大主教和年輕一代\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cardinal Sullivan and the younger generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.71,0:27:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不相信我們所理解的魔鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}they don't believe in the devil as we understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對他們來說那只是概念 對我們來說是真實的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's only an idea for them. For us, it is very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.56,0:27:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,200個墮落的天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Two hundred fallen angels,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.56,0:27:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被逐出天堂 被驅趕到土地之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}expelled from heaven, driven beneath the soil where God is not welcomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.23,0:27:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是童話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It is not a fairytale.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.23,0:27:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你對真理的探索是令人欽佩的 加布裏爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your search for truth is delightful, Gabriele,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.15,0:27:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但要注意你的教育意願\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}but pay attention to your desire to educate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.07,0:27:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,驕傲有不同的表現形式\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Pride manifests itself in different forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.04,0:27:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,驕傲？我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Pride? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.92,0:27:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個案例需要你的關注\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}There's a case that needs your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.00,0:27:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一個在西班牙的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A boy in Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事讓我很不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Something about it disturbs me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.85,0:28:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子的附身進展得非常快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This boy's possession is progressing very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事發地點在聖地\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The incident took place in hallowed ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,卡斯蒂利亞的聖塞巴斯蒂安修道院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}San Sebastian Abbey in Castile.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.86,0:28:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方以前給教會帶來了問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This place has given the Church problems before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺到一股巨大的邪氣從那裏傳來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I sense a great evil coming from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.62,0:28:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你能幫助解決的黑暗力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Something dark that only you can help solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.04,0:28:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我已要求將修道院的記錄帶到圖書館給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have requested the abbey's records be brought to you in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.46,0:28:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,調查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會在你前去途中繼續調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will continue investigating while you're on your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.97,0:28:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你們的罪必追上你們
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.85,0:28:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,「你們的罪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Our sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.64,0:28:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,必追上你們 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}will seek us out."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.06,0:28:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去西班牙幫助這個孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Go to Spain, and help this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.49,0:29:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但要小心 聽起來這個惡魔很危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But be careful, this demon sounds dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.21,0:30:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你好？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.29,0:30:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 我是托馬斯·埃斯奎貝爾神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Good morning. I'm Father Tomas Esquibel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.63,0:30:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-西班牙語？-對\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Spanish? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.71,0:30:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿莫斯神父 意大利人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am Father Amorth. Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.30,0:30:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 阿莫斯神父？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Wait. Father Amorth? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.81,0:30:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到他們會派你來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I didn't expect them to send you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.14,0:30:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你認識我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.22,0:31:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我讀過所有的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes. I have read all the articles. -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.48,0:31:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-還有書本？ -不 書還沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- And the books? - No, no. No, not the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.78,0:31:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那些書都不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The books are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.82,0:31:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我會看的… -好 我去拿行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- I will read-- - Okay. I'll just get my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你…威士忌？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You, uh...  Whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.91,0:31:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No, no, no. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.62,0:31:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對 這喉嚨痛 還有…灰塵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yeah, this sore throat, the dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.46,0:31:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亞 我們很幸運 教會派人來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Julia, we have been extremely lucky. The Church sent someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.92,0:31:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是這方面的專家 加布裏爾 請進\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}An expert in these matters. Gabriele, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.26,0:31:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Good morning, good morning, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.18,0:31:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I am Father Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我來自羅馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have come from Roma.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.39,0:31:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.18,0:31:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉讓你千里迢迢過來…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm sorry that you came all this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.14,0:31:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道教會為何在關注這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}but I don't even know why the Church is interested in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望我兒子能好起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I just want my son to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.56,0:31:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.48,0:31:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我…有醫生給你答案或安慰了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tell me something, have the doctors given you any answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.07,0:31:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼安慰嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Any comfort?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.99,0:31:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請你至少讓我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you would at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.28,0:31:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}just let me see your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.16,0:32:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以給你意見 然後隨便你怎麼做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I can give you my opinion and you can do with it what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.63,0:32:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,值得一試\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.13,0:32:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好 他在樓上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay. He's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.05,0:32:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Very nice, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.68,0:32:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hello, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.16,0:32:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.08,0:32:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒著嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你的禱告在這裏是沒用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your prayers are worthless here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.60,0:34:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.98,0:34:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你最害怕的事 我是你的終結者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your worst fear. I am your demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.77,0:34:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你為何要附身這孩子？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why are you possessing this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.90,0:34:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因為毀掉如此無辜的肉體感覺真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Because it feels so good to ruin such innocent flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.41,0:34:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我更喜歡挑戰驅魔師的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But I prefer the challenge of an exorcist's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你只會讓你自己終結\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You only serve to diminish yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.66,0:34:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要教訓我 牧師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Don't lecture me, priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼目的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.58,0:34:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.46,0:34:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定知道我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Then you must know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.26,0:34:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的靈魂 以及每一個無恥的罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I know your soul and every shameless sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你說說我的一個罪過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tell me one of my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.27,0:35:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你說不出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.85,0:35:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我的罪已被真正的主\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Because my sins have been absolved by the one true master,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.65,0:35:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 主耶穌基督赦免了 -別提祂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- the Lord Jesus Christ. - Do not speak of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.73,0:35:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕祂？你害怕耶穌基督嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Are you afraid of him? Are you afraid of Jesus Christ?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝不在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.99,0:35:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝是無所不在的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.41,0:35:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,無論你做什麼…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Whatever you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.87,0:35:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為上帝允許才能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}you only do because God allows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.54,0:35:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,祂允許那樣嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Did he allow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.88,0:35:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你在和誰打交道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You don't know who you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.89,0:35:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就告訴我 告訴我你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Then tell me. Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.22,0:35:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你太害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Unless you are too afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.81,0:35:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那些會被你說服而附身在豬的蠢貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm not some stupid fuck you convince to get into a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.69,0:35:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼你不肯告訴我你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So you won't tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.40,0:35:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫褻瀆神明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My name is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.98,0:36:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫噩夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My name is nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.95,0:36:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的噩夢…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.46,0:36:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是法國贏得世界盃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}is France winning the World Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個驕傲的傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You prideful fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.38,0:36:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能永遠躲在你的笑話後面…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You can't hide behind your jokes forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.67,0:36:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.93,0:36:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道你的噩夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I know your nightmares too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.08,0:36:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧 膽小鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Show yourself, coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.50,0:36:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,出來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.29,0:36:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.63,0:37:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,出來 懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Show yourself, coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.86,0:37:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,當心 你的罪必追上你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Beware, your sins will seek you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我會等你的 加布\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'll be waiting for you, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.41,0:37:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你有沒有向這屋裏的任何人提過我的名字？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Did you mention my name to anyone in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.54,0:37:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有 我不肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Maybe, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.21,0:37:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡魔… 它說了它不該知道的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This demon, it says things that it could not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.05,0:37:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 它是真的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.05,0:37:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你對惡魔的瞭解有多少？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What do you know about demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.51,0:37:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有基礎知識 他們是墮落的天使\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Only the basics, that they are fallen angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.85,0:37:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以著等級制度 一個服侍著另一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}One serves the other in a hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.23,0:38:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等級越高的惡魔 它能侵入的管道越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The higher the demon, the more access it can have.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它為何要附身那個男孩？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So why is it possessing the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.78,0:38:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個好問題 我會和他母親談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is a very good question. I'm going to talk to the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.45,0:38:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要弄清楚這惡魔為什麼選擇亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I need to work out why this demon has chosen Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.91,0:38:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下來要說的話… 也許很難接受 正視它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What I am about to say may be difficult. Confronting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.33,0:38:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的兒子被一個非常強大的惡魔附身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your son is under the influence of a very powerful demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,帶走這孩子可能會致命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Removing the boy from this place could be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.05,0:38:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我跟你說…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I say to you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.51,0:38:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你兒子回到你身邊的唯一方法 就是藉著信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}the only way your son comes back to you is through faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.98,0:38:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦斯克斯太太 亨利之前是否出了什麼事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Mrs. Vasquez, did anything happen to Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.61,0:38:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他遭遇了殺死他父親的車禍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He was in the car accident that killed his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.74,0:38:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他看到他父親被刺穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He saw his father impaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.28,0:38:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那段記憶… 那就是他的惡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That memory, that's his demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.21,0:38:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I give you my word,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會離棄你或你兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will not walk away from you, or your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.05,0:39:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,正如你所說 那種創傷可能是魔鬼附身的途徑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Trauma such as you describe can be a gateway for the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.09,0:39:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,苦難會讓一個靈魂渴望聯繫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Suffering can make a soul desperate for connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.31,0:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它會使無辜者更加脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It can make the innocent more vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.94,0:39:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前一定十分愛你的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You must have loved your husband very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.70,0:39:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,非常愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.53,0:39:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是你的靈魂聯繫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He was your soul connection, si?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.41,0:39:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He was everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你有兩個漂亮的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And you have two beautiful children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽的愛… 是最接近上帝之愛的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A mother's love is the closest thing we know to God's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.01,0:39:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 茱莉亞…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tell me, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.18,0:40:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾相信過嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Have you ever believed?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.65,0:40:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Uh, when I was a little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.86,0:40:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經以為我的守護天使陪我上學\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I used to think that my guardian angel walked me to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.37,0:40:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該向那個守護天使禱告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You should pray to that guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.55,0:40:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.15,0:40:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.54,0:41:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.17,0:41:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我在地獄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 親愛的 是爸爸 你一定要聽 好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, honey, it's Dad. You have to listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.98,0:41:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.11,0:41:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都會死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You're all going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.91,0:41:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.41,0:41:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 是爸爸 是爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Mom, it was Daddy. It was Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.99,0:41:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽見爸爸的聲音 我在電話裏聽見他的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I heard Dad's voice. I heard his voice on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.66,0:41:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-他說我們都會死 -什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- He said that we're all gonna die. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.42,0:41:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-他說我們都會死 -天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- He said that we were all gonna die. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.51,0:41:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.38,0:41:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.01,0:42:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那些惡魔在夜晚會更強大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The demons, they grow more strongly in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.22,0:42:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要能量 但你應該盡量休息一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm going to need my energy. But you should try to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.31,0:42:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,願所有逝去的信徒的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And may the souls of all the faithful departed,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.02,0:42:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在上帝的憐憫下 安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}through the mercy of God, rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.86,0:42:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿門 -這需要多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Amen. -  How long will this take?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.61,0:42:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那很難說\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That is hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.11,0:42:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,幾個小時\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.16,0:42:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也許幾天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Days, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡魔很強\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This demon is very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.45,0:42:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子撐不了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The boy won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.58,0:42:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該做的事…就是找出它的名字才能驅魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What we need to do is to find out its name in order to exorcize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.88,0:42:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我們能拯救那孩子的唯一方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That is the only way we can save the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.75,0:42:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼做？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.42,0:42:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以著禱告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}With prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.97,0:42:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷的祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Constant prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.63,0:42:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,惡魔… 它們是自保的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The demons, they are self-preserving.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.80,0:42:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不瞭解痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They do not understand suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.85,0:42:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,最終 它會投降\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Eventually, he will give himself up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.93,0:42:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它無法忍受禱告的痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}because he cannot stand the pain of the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.27,0:42:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.77,0:42:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes. - Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.48,0:42:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-現在你必須懺悔你的罪過 -現在？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Now, you must confess your sins. - Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.40,0:42:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒有被赦免 惡魔能聞到你的罪孽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The demon can smell your sins if they are not absolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.99,0:42:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.66,0:43:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.04,0:43:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我 神父…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Forgive me, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.29,0:43:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我犯了罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}for I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.54,0:43:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,自從…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It has been, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.87,0:43:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-我上次告白已八個月… -神父 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- eight months since my last confession-- - Padre, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.13,0:43:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說你距離上次告白已八個月了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Did you just say eight months since your last confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.21,0:43:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 -我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes. - I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.38,0:43:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們一定要做好這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay, we just have to get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.18,0:43:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是神的僕人 夠簡單的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- You are a man of God, simple enough, si? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.14,0:43:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你為你所有的罪過感到非常抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And you are very, very sorry for all of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.06,0:43:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Yes. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.48,0:43:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,願全能的神憐憫你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}May almighty God have mercy on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.35,0:43:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,並且赦免了你的罪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and having forgiven your sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.11,0:43:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帶領你走向永恆的和平  阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}lead you to eternal peace. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.36,0:43:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道哪些驅魔儀式？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What rites of the exorcism do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.66,0:43:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒有 -沒有？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- None. - None?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.74,0:43:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,從來沒談論過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It has never come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.91,0:43:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哪些禱告是你即使在壓力下也能持續地做的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What prayer do you know that you could say over and over, even under pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.00,0:43:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,聖母經\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Hail Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.46,0:43:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果在壓力之下 我比較喜歡用西班牙語說\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But if it is under pressure, I would prefer to say it in Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.75,0:43:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.67,0:44:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任務…就是禱告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your job is to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.22,0:44:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要與惡魔接觸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do not engage with the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.26,0:44:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要回應它所說或所做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do not respond to anything it says or does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.93,0:44:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任務是堅持不懈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your job is to be implacabile.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.18,0:44:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持不懈 知道嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Relentless. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.32,0:44:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你會說笑話嗎？-不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- You know any jokes? - Eh... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.82,0:44:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該學一些 魔鬼不喜歡笑話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You should learn some. The devil does not like jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.03,0:44:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把書帶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Bring the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.16,0:44:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂的氣味\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The scent of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.95,0:44:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你把朋友帶來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I see you've brought your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他看來有點害怕 加布\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He looks a little scared, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.38,0:44:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,介意我叫你加布嗎 加布？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Mind if I call you Gabe, Gabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.51,0:44:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好戰鬥了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Readying for battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.68,0:44:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,上次你逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You ran out on me last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.01,0:44:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像個懦夫 小士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}like the coward you are, soldier boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.97,0:44:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不太適合成為首席驅魔師\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Not very becoming of the chief exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.06,0:44:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你打算被誰征服 耶穌還是祂媽媽？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Who do you want to be vanquished by today, Jesus or his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.69,0:44:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋的聖母\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Fuck the Holy Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.07,0:45:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是要談一整夜還是你想戰鬥？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Are we going to talk all night, or do you want to battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.15,0:45:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我要對你做什麼嗎 加布裏爾？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Know what I'm going to do to you, Gabriele?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.45,0:45:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我會睡了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I'm going to fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.70,0:45:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你會感覺到高潮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You'll sense yourself coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.41,0:45:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然後你會因為我睡你時的釋放… 而恨自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And you'll hate yourself for the release you feel when I fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.25,0:45:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我們祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And now we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.34,0:45:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你 污鬼 無論你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I command you, unclean spirit, whoever you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.97,0:45:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,以及現在你所有攻擊著上帝的僕人 亨利的爪牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}along with all of your minions now attacking the servant of God, Henry,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.55,0:45:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,藉著道成肉身的奧秘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}by the mysteries of the incarnation...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.60,0:45:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-去你的的化身 -受難 復活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Fuck you and your incarnations. - ...passion, resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.10,0:45:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們主耶穌基督的升天 藉著聖靈的降臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and ascension of our Lord Jesus Christ, by the descent of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.44,0:45:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,藉著我們主的降臨施行審判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}by the coming of our Lord for judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.78,0:45:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你用某種跡象告訴我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to tell me by some sign
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.57,0:45:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名以及你離開的日期和時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}your name and the day and hour of your departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.78,0:45:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas, pray. Pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.57,0:45:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,此外 我命令你 確實服從我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I command you, moreover, to obey me to the letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管我不配 但我是上帝的牧師…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I who am a minister of God, despite my unworthiness--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.36,0:46:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,羅莎莉亞？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Rosaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.07,0:46:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的罪必追上你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your sins will seek you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.57,0:46:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的罪已經被赦免了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My sins have been forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.65,0:46:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能原諒自己 不是嗎 神父？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But you can't forgive yourself, can you, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.70,0:46:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是為了我… 那個你任由她死去的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Not for me, the girl you let die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.62,0:46:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼什麼都不做？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why did you do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.29,0:46:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不相信我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why didn't you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.71,0:46:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 我在地獄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Now I am in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.92,0:46:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Deceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.09,0:46:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她的靈魂安息了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Her soul rests in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.34,0:46:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的靈魂在地獄裏腐爛著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My soul rots in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.15,0:47:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真感人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.86,0:47:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有這些嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.20,0:47:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢 嗅內褲的？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And how about you, panty sniffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.83,0:47:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒告訴他吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You didn't tell him, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.70,0:47:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,關於你的小妓女？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}About your little whore?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.29,0:47:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小甜心 阿黛拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your little sweet treat, Adella.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.42,0:47:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你站在你的會眾面前 就像你比他們更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}After you stood before your congregation like you're better than them,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.09,0:47:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,同時又在上他們的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}when you're fucking their daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.80,0:47:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你對那個罪並沒有那麼難過？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Maybe you aren't so sorry about that sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.26,0:47:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.14,0:47:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 不要和它說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas. Tomas. Do not speak to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.81,0:47:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-祈禱 -快逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Pray. - Run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.39,0:47:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想待在這裏 托馬斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You don't want to be here, Tomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.10,0:47:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你寧願和那個小婊子上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You'd rather be fucking that little whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.52,0:47:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 不要 不 那就是它的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas! Tomas! No! No, no! That's what it wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.99,0:47:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你被耍了 阿莫斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You've been played, Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.87,0:48:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你上當了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You took the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.67,0:48:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我會毀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And I'll destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.63,0:48:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你的神聖教會將從內部崩潰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your holy Church will crumble from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.94,0:48:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,修道院的記錄 教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The abbey's records, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.31,0:49:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我一生的摯愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}She was the love of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.41,0:49:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我做出了承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A promise was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.16,0:49:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她要我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}She wanted me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.91,0:49:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,為了她放下聖職\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}leave the priesthood for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.67,0:49:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}but I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.04,0:49:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,無意那樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.63,0:49:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就告訴她她想聽的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So I just told her what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.81,0:49:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我對上帝的愛…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}My love for God...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.40,0:49:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,超過了我對她的愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}it outweighed my love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.02,0:49:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你為自己的罪過感到難過嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Are you sorry for your sins?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.69,0:49:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.11,0:49:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,願全能的上帝憐憫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}May almighty God show you mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.61,0:49:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,並且赦免了你的罪過\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And having forgiven your sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.33,0:50:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,願祂帶領你進入永生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}may he lead you to eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.54,0:50:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.29,0:50:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.55,0:50:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.09,0:50:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,羅莎莉亞？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Rosaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.93,0:50:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一個我本該幫助的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}She is a girl that I should've helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.94,0:50:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,惡魔利用她的記憶來欺騙我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The demon is using her memory to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.10,0:50:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,它是怎麼知道這些事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}How does it know these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.90,0:50:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它能感覺到我們的罪惡感\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It can sense our guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.40,0:50:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,並利用它來對付我們 讓我們分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and it uses it against us as a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.66,0:50:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那個男孩 他就快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That boy, he does not have long before he expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.99,0:50:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須找出這惡魔的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We need to find out the name of this demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.25,0:50:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,找出它的名字會使他們變弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Knowing its name, it weakens them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.33,0:50:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是有意傷害他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I didn't mean to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.09,0:50:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.38,0:50:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}See here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.46,0:50:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經替你標記這一頁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have marked this page for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.80,0:50:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,去學它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Learn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.55,0:51:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但它是拉丁文\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But it is in Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.64,0:51:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蠻像西班牙語的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Close enough to Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.72,0:51:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,用拉丁語祈禱更有力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Prayer has more power in Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.98,0:51:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,「你上當了 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"You have taken the bait."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.73,0:51:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼？ -它對我說的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- What? - What it said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,「你上當了 阿莫斯 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"You have taken the bait, Amorth."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.16,0:51:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這和那孩子無關\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is not about the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.16,0:51:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它有更大的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It has a bigger plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.66,0:51:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要檢查一些我在花園裏看到的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I need to check something I saw in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.46,0:51:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去 拿著這個 站在他門外 他還沒脫離危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Go. Take this. Be outside his door. He is still in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.96,0:51:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一定要盡全力保護他 做你該做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We must protect him at all cost. Do whatever you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.27,0:51:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,梵蒂岡的印章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The seal of the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.65,0:51:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這地方以前給教會帶來了問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This place has given the Church problems before.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.72,0:53:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝 奉禰的名…拯救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God, by your name... save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.93,0:53:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,幫助我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.11,0:53:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.71,0:54:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.11,0:54:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人能活著離開這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No one's getting out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.57,0:54:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.08,0:55:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你隱藏了什麼秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Let's see what secrets you are hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.03,0:56:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.70,0:56:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.43,0:56:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.55,0:56:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amorth!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.43,0:56:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.56,0:56:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.10,0:56:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.31,0:56:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,以主的名義 讓她走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the name of Christ, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,以主的名義 讓她走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the name of Christ, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.28,0:56:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.82,0:56:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.32,0:56:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以主的名義 讓她走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the name of Christ, let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.20,0:56:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's me. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.62,0:56:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 艾米\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Oh, my God. Oh, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.37,0:57:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以主的名義 走開 撒旦 走開\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the name of Christ, go away, Satan, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.93,0:57:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是她的一個指甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's one of her nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.44,0:57:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 帶他們去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas, take them to the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.95,0:57:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一切已被節錄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Everything is redacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.63,0:57:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"你們的罪必追上你們"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Our sins will seek us out."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.88,0:57:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,「你們的罪必追上你們 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Our sins will seek us out."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.81,0:58:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-你還好嗎？ -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Are you okay? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.48,0:58:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個行業無法允許你保持帥氣太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You don't get to stay handsome in this business for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.73,0:58:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Please. Hm? Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.32,0:58:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有個惡魔試圖把一個十字架放入我的眼球\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I once have a demon try to put a crucifix into my eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.32,0:58:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你總是一直說 夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You're always talking and talking. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.20,0:58:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.83,0:58:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They're sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.33,0:58:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別再說什麼故事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No more stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.92,0:58:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否想過惡魔為何要這樣？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Did you consider why the demon does this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.46,0:58:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們害怕？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To scare us, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.84,0:58:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為了什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}For what benefit?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.72,0:58:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,混亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.34,0:58:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,分心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.59,0:58:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼是大騙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The devil is the great deceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.72,0:58:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他能讓你看到過去的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He can make you see things from your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.93,0:58:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幻象 回憶 總是試圖欺騙我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Apparitions, memories, always trying to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.81,0:58:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣我們永遠不知道它在想什麼 計劃什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So we never know what he's thinking, what he's planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不相信我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}If you do not believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.40,0:58:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,問我朋友吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}just ask my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.74,0:59:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來 我帶你去看我的發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Come, I'll show you what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.87,0:59:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amorth!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.46,0:59:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛到的時候注意到了這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I noticed this when I first arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.21,0:59:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.00,0:59:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你認得這個嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.26,0:59:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是西班牙宗教裁判所的標誌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, it's the seal of the Spanish Inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.43,0:59:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,基督徒史上最黑暗的時期\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Si. The darkest time in the history of the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.18,0:59:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而他們是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And they are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.47,0:59:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,受害者 那些不皈依的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The victims. The ones who would not convert.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.81,0:59:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方下面有東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}There is something underneath this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.36,0:59:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏隱藏著一些東西  來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Something is hidden here. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.13,1:00:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.27,1:00:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個交叉的鑰匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Two crossed keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.44,1:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你認得這個嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do you recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.15,1:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是梵蒂岡印章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- It's the Vatican seal. -
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.07,1:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-是氣體嗎？- 一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Is it gas? -  A little gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.78,1:00:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,少許硫磺 一點死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A little sulfur. A little death.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.74,1:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 不可抽煙？退後\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So no smoking, huh?  Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.26,1:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個門 跟我一起推\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's a door. Push with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.01,1:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.07,1:01:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,地下墓穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Catacomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.70,1:01:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是他們埋葬死者的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This is how they would bury the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.63,1:01:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道梵蒂岡封鎖了這個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I understand the Vatican sealing this place off.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.55,1:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他們為什麼要留下一個人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But why would they leave someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.26,1:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大主教保護者的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The ring of the cardinal protector.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.86,1:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他是最後的希望 最後的保護者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He was the final hope, the last protector.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.65,1:01:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來他是個囚犯 但他不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It looks like he's a prisoner, but he's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.12,1:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,籠子是為了他自己的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The cage is for his own safety.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.99,1:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他們這樣做…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}They do this when an exorcism fails.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.21,1:01:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就是驅魔失敗的時候 為了防止惡魔逃脫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To protect against a demon's escape,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.92,1:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,困住他們需要隱藏的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to trap something they need to remain hidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.76,1:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 看看你能不能打開這扇門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas, see if you can open this gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.19,1:02:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的大主教保護者寫信通知你 我們最擔心的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Your cardinal protector writes to inform you of our worst fears.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.11,1:02:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一個強大的邪惡已佔據了聖塞巴斯蒂安修道院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A great evil has taken hold of San Sebastian Abbey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.07,1:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它必須永遠被埋葬在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It must be buried here forever."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.83,1:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,鎖上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.37,1:02:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們這個朋友…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Then our friend here...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.96,1:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有鑰匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}must have a key.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.76,1:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你把鑰匙藏在那裏了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Where did you hide your key?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.05,1:02:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在肚子裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.52,1:02:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.99,1:03:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,試這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Try this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.04,1:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.34,1:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的驅魔行動都失敗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"All attempts at exorcism have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這地方是屬撒旦的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Satan owns this ground now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.34,1:03:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過 如此強大的惡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have never seen a demon this powerful before."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.86,1:03:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.07,1:03:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.46,1:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.88,1:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thank you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.73,1:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.58,1:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那些氣體和硫磺 越來越強了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The gases and the sulfur, it's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.75,1:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們離地獄越來越近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We are getting closer to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.14,1:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沙利文大主教 他還好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cardinal Sullivan, is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.39,1:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他昏倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.65,1:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Holy Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.94,1:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是情緒激動\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You are just agitated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.95,1:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.49,1:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴誰？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tell who?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.03,1:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.87,1:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.71,1:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amorth?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.25,1:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莫斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amorth?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.50,1:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這一次他又害我們惹什麼麻煩了？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What trouble has he got us into this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.67,1:05:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,德奧哈達修士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Friar De Ojada.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.93,1:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有史以來最偉大的驅魔人之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}One of the greatest exorcists of all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.23,1:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,西班牙宗教裁判所的標誌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The seal of the Spanish Inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.70,1:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他的日記\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}His journal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.28,1:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,「今天 我被召喚到塞哥維亞小鎮 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Today...I was summoned to the town of Segovia."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.12,1:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一個被附身的僧人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A possessed monk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.75,1:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,「在我們主的那年 1475年…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"In the year of our Lord 1475.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.21,1:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在審問附身僧人的惡魔時\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}While questioning the demon possessing the monk,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他從另一個人的口中回答我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}he answered me from the mouth of another.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.67,1:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是第三個 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And then a third."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.05,1:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,附身多人 是個強大的惡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Multiple possessions. It's a powerful demon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.49,1:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.42,1:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,「驅魔人著了魔 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"The exorcist becomes possessed himself."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.80,1:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,德奧哈達修士？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Friar De Ojada?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.01,1:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他是說服伊莎貝拉女王…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You know he is the man who convinced Queen Isabella
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.81,1:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,成立宗教裁判所之必要性的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}of the need for an Inquisition?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.31,1:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這意味著他在1475年被附身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So that means from the time he is possessed in 1475,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.44,1:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這之後發生的一切…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}everything that happens after this...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.61,1:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是魔鬼的傑作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}is the work of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.61,1:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,幾個世紀的迫害和折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Centuries of persecution and torture,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.83,1:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宗教裁判所最嚴重的濫用職權\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}the worst abuses of the Inquisition,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.08,1:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一切由修士以上帝的名義開始…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}all started by the friar and done in the name of God
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.41,1:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都是魔鬼做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}by the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.33,1:07:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,梵蒂岡一定知道這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Vatican must have known this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.63,1:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,教會掩蓋了這事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Church covered it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.38,1:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,並把真相埋在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And they buried the truth here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.46,1:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,「你們的罪必追上你們 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Your sins will seek you out."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.47,1:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是建築工程釋放了惡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The construction work must have freed the demon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.14,1:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.27,1:07:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.73,1:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.61,1:08:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- It's okay, Mommy. - It's okay, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.74,1:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Henry's okay. - Henry's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.91,1:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.24,1:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好 艾米 不然你跟我到樓下去吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Listen, Amy, why don't you come downstairs with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.29,1:08:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- I'm sorry, Mom. - I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.00,1:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我被什麼附身了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- I don't know what got into me. - I don't know what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.79,1:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.30,1:08:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我只是…我只需要你姐姐一會兒 艾米…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That's okay. I just need your sister for a minute. Amy?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.42,1:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你能原諒我嗎 媽媽？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Can you forgive me, Mom? - Can you forgive me, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.73,1:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「大龍被摔在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"The great dragon was hurled down.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.90,1:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,被驅逐到地上 把它捆綁在地 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Hurled into the earth, where he was bound."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.69,1:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,「它的使者跟著它 」啟示錄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"And his angels with him." Revelations.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.78,1:08:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,兩百個狂暴天使埋入地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Two hundred rogue angels buried into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.04,1:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個修道院是那些被神遺忘的地方之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This abbey is one of those godforsaken places.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.04,1:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡魔 它試圖找出它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This demon, he was trying to find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.54,1:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,以募集軍隊並摧毀教會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To raise an army and destroy the Church.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.34,1:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.71,1:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上拿著什麼 媽媽？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- What's in your hand, Mommy? - What's in your hand, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.80,1:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 過來 馬上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, come here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.09,1:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上拿著什麼 媽媽？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- What's in your hand, Mommy? - What's in your hand, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.82,1:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.28,1:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看我 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Watch me, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.62,1:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.30,1:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它的名字…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}His name...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.39,1:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,地獄之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}the king of hell...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.93,1:09:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阿斯蒙蒂斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Asmodeus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.24,1:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.91,1:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米 用鎮定劑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amy, use the sedative.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.33,1:10:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把他的手綁起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tie his arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.39,1:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道它的名字了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We have his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.77,1:10:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,「把牧師帶來 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Bring me the priest."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.57,1:10:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛說什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.90,1:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這是惡魔說的第一句話 "把牧師帶來"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Those were the first words the demon said. "Bring me the priest."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.20,1:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它說的不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It didn't mean me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.16,1:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,它要的是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It wants you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.62,1:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這個惡魔以附身驅魔人為生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This demon feeds on exorcists.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.66,1:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它曾經有過一個計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He had a plan once.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.62,1:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把修士引誘到這裏…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To lure the friar here,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.29,1:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏在正義中 以上帝的名做出令人髮指的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}hide amongst the righteous and commit heinous acts in the name of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.34,1:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他想再次做同樣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He wants to do the same thing again.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.63,1:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,利用我潛入教會\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Using me to infiltrate the Church.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.47,1:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,魔鬼最大的勝利…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What greater victory for the devil...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.47,1:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奪得教皇驅魔人的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}than to claim the soul of the pope's exorcist?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.77,1:11:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是 但現在我們知道它的名字了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Maybe. But we know his name now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.77,1:11:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們已有擊敗它和拯救那孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So we have what we need to beat it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.78,1:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所需的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and to save the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.40,1:11:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能打敗我們的就是我們自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The only thing that can defeat us is ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.58,1:11:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他會利用你的罪來對付你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He will use your sins against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.79,1:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須認罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I need to make confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.21,1:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-向我？-你不是牧師嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- To me? - You are a priest, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.67,1:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我 神父 因為我犯了罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Forgive me, Father, for I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.18,1:11:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,倚靠耶和華\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Trust in the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.81,1:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你談談…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I want to talk to you...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.98,1:12:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,關於我之前已認罪…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}about things I have confessed before...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.77,1:12:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但仍然給我帶來負擔的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}but they still burden me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.57,1:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在1942年…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In 1942...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.53,1:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,戰爭期間 我加入了抵抗組織\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}during the war, I joined the Resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.70,1:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我成為游擊隊員 並與法西斯分子作戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I became a partisan and I fought against the fascists.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.99,1:12:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我很多戰友都死於德國人槍下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So many of my friends would die to German bullets.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.83,1:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是他們…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Why them...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.13,1:12:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是我？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and not me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.26,1:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的屍體會在夢中跟我說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Their dead bodies would talk to me in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.47,1:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,戰死沙場是英勇的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To die in a war is heroic.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.76,1:12:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在戰爭後存活…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To survive a war...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.60,1:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是複雜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}complex.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.69,1:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我開始體會…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And then I begin to see...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.77,1:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生命得以倖免\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}that my life had been spared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.61,1:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我有責任賦予它生存的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It was my responsibility to give it purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.28,1:12:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就我而言 這意味著侍奉上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And in my case, that meant to serve God.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.82,1:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多年來 我一直在努力接受馬太福音中所說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In all of my years, I have tried to embrace what is said in Matthew.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.79,1:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,「你為你們當中最少的人所做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"What you do for the least among you,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.34,1:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為我做的 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}you do for me."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.50,1:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在重要時刻…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But when it mattered...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.92,1:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我失敗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.01,1:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有幫助她 或相信她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I did not help her, I did not believe her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.64,1:13:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不聽她的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I did not listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.68,1:13:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,羅莎莉亞？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Rosaria?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.94,1:13:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,羅莎莉亞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Rosaria.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.65,1:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上 魔鬼會和我上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}At night, the devil fucks me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.32,1:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡魔長什麼樣子？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What does this devil look like?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.95,1:13:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,像你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.54,1:13:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒有被附身…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}She was not possessed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.34,1:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她是神經錯亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}She was mentally disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.96,1:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我讓別人處理她的案件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So I let someone else handle her case.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.26,1:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Again...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.76,1:13:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的傲氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}my pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.22,1:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是驅魔人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I was an exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.97,1:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,精神錯亂的人不關我的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The mentally disturbed, it's not my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.10,1:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你相信我嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do you believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.69,1:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但那一切就因為她…而改變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But that all changed because of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.66,1:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說 在她死後\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To hear after her death
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.79,1:14:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那些性虐待的謠言 遮掩的行為\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}the rumors of the sexual abuse, the coverup
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.16,1:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都在梵蒂岡城牆內\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}within the walls of the Vatican City.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.09,1:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那無辜的女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}That innocent girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.42,1:14:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在她需要我時沒有幫助她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I did not help her when she needed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.51,1:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她的靈魂…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Her soul
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.60,1:14:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的負擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}is my burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.14,1:14:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這個惡魔 它知道這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And this demon, he knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.23,1:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我所認識的你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I know you...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.86,1:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,作為上帝謙卑的人… 阿莫斯神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}as a humble man of God, Father Amorth.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.74,1:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候放下這個負擔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It's time to lay down that burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.16,1:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我 天父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Forgive me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.04,1:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉聖父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I absolve you of your sins
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.29,1:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聖子和聖靈之名 赦免你的罪孽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}in the name of the Father, of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.05,1:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.45,1:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你奇跡勳章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I give you the miraculous medal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.12,1:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,聖火保險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Holy fire insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.08,1:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.67,1:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要打敗地獄之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To defeat the king of hell...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.47,1:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要上帝的盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}we require the armor of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.01,1:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要打敗地獄之王\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}To defeat the king of hell...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.72,1:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要上帝的盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}we require the armor of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.62,1:16:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,記住 惡魔會利用你的感官來對付你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Remember, the demon will use your sins against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.00,1:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要相信你看到或聽到的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Do not believe everything you see or hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.71,1:16:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.92,1:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須救這孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We must save this child.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.04,1:17:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都告白罪了嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}All done confessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.30,1:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.38,1:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他向你袒露他的靈魂了嗎 托馬斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Did he bare his soul to you, Tomas?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.01,1:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的小妓女那樣露出她的乳房？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Like your little whore bared her breasts?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.68,1:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別理它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.06,1:17:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為亨利祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Pray for Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.31,1:17:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再多的祈禱也救不了亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}No amount of prayers can save Henry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.56,1:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我進去 加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Let me in, Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.77,1:17:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我要什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.32,1:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在… 天上的父…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Our Father, who art in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.36,1:17:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-願禰的名受顯揚 -願禰的國降臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- In heaven, hallowed be thy name. - ...hallowed be thy name.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.82,1:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,願禰的旨意… -向你的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thy kingdom come, thy...
