Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.03,1:26:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要我的豬把我帶到梵蒂岡 加布\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I need my pig to get me inside the Vatican, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.13,1:27:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.85,1:27:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的我們倆…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Damn us both...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.35,1:27:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都下地獄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.22,1:27:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.65,1:28:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.09,1:28:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你太遲了 托馬斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You're too late, Tomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.93,1:28:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了 你的朋友 死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He's gone, your friend. Gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.68,1:28:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.23,1:28:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}run along.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.78,1:28:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我很榮幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It would be my great pleasure
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.77,1:28:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能摧毀你的靈魂 並剔除你的記憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}to excoriate your soul and eviscerate your memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.82,1:28:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾 聽我說 抵制它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele, listen to me. Fight it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.79,1:28:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是在你腦海裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It is just in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.46,1:28:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只能被自己打敗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}We can only be defeated by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.08,1:28:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}He is not here!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.70,1:29:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小豬在地獄的水槽裏撒潑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The little piggy is slopping at hell's trough,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.96,1:29:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他所屬的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.71,1:29:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你還在 加布裏爾 跟我一起祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I know you're here, Gabriele. Pray with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.59,1:29:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝不在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is not here!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.51,1:29:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝一直在我們心裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is always in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.80,1:29:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,專心祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Focus on the prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.52,1:29:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,「當有兩個人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}"Where two of you gather...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.89,1:29:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奉我的名聚會…那裏就有我 」\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}in my name, there am I."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.10,1:29:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求主憐憫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Lord, have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.23,1:29:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧 求主憐憫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Say it! Lord, have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.07,1:29:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝與你同在 加布裏爾 尋找它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God is with you, Gabriele. Find him!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.45,1:29:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,了結它 托馬斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Finish it, Tomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.91,1:29:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,了結它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Finish it!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.20,1:29:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊 奉禰的名 拯救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}God, by your name, save me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.33,1:29:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,憑禰的大能為我伸冤\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Judge me in thy strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.67,1:29:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,神阿 求禰聽我的禱告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}O God, hear my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.80,1:29:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,留心聽我口中的言語\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Listen to the words of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.93,1:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,神是我的幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Behold, God is my helper.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.14,1:30:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄吧 他是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Give up. He is mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.48,1:30:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你以無瑕羔羊的名義\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I adjure you in the name of the spotless lamb.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.52,1:30:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,話語道成了肉身命令你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The word made flesh commands you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.11,1:30:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阿斯蒙蒂斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Asmodeus!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.65,1:30:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拿撒勒人耶穌命令你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Jesus of Nazareth commands you!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.65,1:30:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 我以祂的名義命令你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And now, I adjure you in his name!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.16,1:30:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 聽我的禱告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Lord, heed my prayer!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.87,1:30:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-說 -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Say it! - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.38,1:30:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 加布裏爾 -我們還沒來個了斷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Gabriele. - We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.59,1:30:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們會下地獄的 牧師們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You're coming to hell, priests.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.97,1:30:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我會帶你們倆去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will take you both.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.89,1:30:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,阿黛拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Adella.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.13,1:31:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的罪必追上…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Your sins will seek...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.34,1:31:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,必追上你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Seek you out!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.71,1:31:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 用勳章\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas, use the medal!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.59,1:31:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 賜予我力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Lord, grant me the power!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.40,1:31:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.90,1:31:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,以聖母之名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Asmodeus. In the name of the Holy Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.65,1:31:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,降伏於上帝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}See thee beneath God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.41,1:31:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,降伏於上帝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}See thee beneath God!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.42,1:31:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,托馬斯 祈禱最後的儀式\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Tomas! Pray the final rites.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.58,1:31:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奉聖父…聖子 聖靈之名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}In the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.30,1:31:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,降伏於上帝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}see thee beneath God!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.95,1:32:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾 你還好嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.41,1:32:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.29,1:32:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-托馬斯 -什麼？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- Tomas. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.55,1:32:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You look like shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.97,1:32:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,神祝福你 托馬斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Bless you, Tomas.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.43,1:32:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你學會了拉丁語\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You learned the Latin.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.93,1:32:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 它和西班牙語很相似\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, it's similar to the Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.73,1:32:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和西班牙語非常相似\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Very similar to the Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.48,1:32:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.07,1:33:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 上帝…的作為… 是何等奧秘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You know, the God, he works in very mysterious ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.21,1:33:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}For you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.64,1:33:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 的確是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.15,1:33:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咕咕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cuckoo.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.74,1:33:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是你嗎 加布裏爾？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Is that you, Gabriele?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.83,1:33:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 教皇陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yes, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.87,1:33:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了埃斯基貝爾神父來見你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And I have brought Padre Esquibel to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.96,1:33:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來很好 教皇陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You look well, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.62,1:33:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 很高興見到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thanks to you both. I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.00,1:33:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這一次你讓我擔心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You had me worried this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.46,1:34:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來很危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Sounded dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.09,1:34:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 還不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Yeah, not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.93,1:34:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有時你飛得離太陽有點太近了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Sometimes you fly a little too close to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.64,1:34:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒被殺死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}It has not killed me yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.31,1:34:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,教會不會忘記你所做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Church will not forget what you have done.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.60,1:34:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你給了我們一個沉重的打擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You struck a mighty blow for our side.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.48,1:34:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,聖邁克爾會感到自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Saint Michael would be proud.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.07,1:34:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是上帝把你放在這裏的原因 加布裏爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And this is why God put you here, Gabriele.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.36,1:34:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝 教皇陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thank you very much, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.45,1:34:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還有上帝選擇你是正確的 埃斯基貝爾神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And God has made a good choice in you too, Father Esquibel.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.08,1:34:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 教皇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Thank you, Holy Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.49,1:34:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,會眾要求提供有關西班牙的完整報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The congregation has requested a full report on Spain.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.96,1:34:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一個完整的報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}A full report.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.42,1:34:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讓沙利文大主教再告訴我 邪惡只存在於想像嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}So Cardinal Sullivan can tell me again that evil only exists in my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.26,1:34:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒聽說？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.84,1:34:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沙利文大主教在關島休假\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Cardinal Sullivan has taken a sabbatical in the Isle of Guam.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.14,1:34:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要為…關島祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I shall pray for Guam.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.48,1:34:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼誰…接替他呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And who has, uh, filled his shoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.98,1:35:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一個更值得信賴的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I have found someone far more trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.11,1:35:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他會好好照顧你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}I will leave you in his good hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.12,1:35:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,降伏於…上帝之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}See thee beneath God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.20,1:35:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,降伏於上帝之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}- See thee beneath God. - See thee beneath God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.00,1:35:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到最神聖的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Welcome to the holiest of holies.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.80,1:35:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,十二個世紀的寶藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Twelve centuries of treasures.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.09,1:35:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,來自聖人和使徒的信件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Letters from saints and apostles.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.68,1:35:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,智慧和虔誠的書籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Books of wisdom and piety.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.43,1:35:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,靈的啟示\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Revelations of the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.85,1:35:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的經典基督教思想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The entire canon of Christian thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.56,1:35:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,梵蒂岡從巴斯克斯家族手中買下修道院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The Vatican has purchased the abbey from the Vasquez family
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.27,1:35:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,並重新祝聖了土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}and reconsecrated the soil.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.36,1:35:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他們一家人安全搬回美國 小孩完全康復\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The family has safely relocated back to the U.S.,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.70,1:35:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他們一家人安全地搬回美國 小孩完全康復\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}where the boy made a full recovery.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.04,1:35:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,事實證明修士的日記很有用 儘管他深惡痛絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}The friar's diary is proving very useful, despite his abhorrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.54,1:36:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,阿斯摩蒂爾斯被擊敗 但還有更多有待發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Asmodeus has been defeated, but there are many more to be found.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.96,1:36:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很快我們就會找出地球上其他199個\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Soon we will know all of the other 199 sites on earth
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.59,1:36:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不歡迎上帝的地點\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}where God is not welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.22,1:36:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加布裏爾 你願意接受這個任務嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Gabriele, will you take on this task?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.77,1:36:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對於一個牧師來說 用一輩子來做也不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}This would be more than a lifetime's work for one priest.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.31,1:36:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但兩個牧師…\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}But two priests...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.53,1:36:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢 托馬斯？ 現在你能把它看作是一種召喚嗎？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}What do you think, Tomas? Can you see this now as a calling?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.20,1:36:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須按照上帝的旨意來侍奉上帝？\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}And that we must serve God the way he wants us to serve him?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.87,1:36:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們開工吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Let's go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.12,1:36:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去地獄吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14}Let's go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.06,1:36:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}加布裏爾阿莫斯神父
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.39,1:36:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(繼續為受苦的人服務 直到2016年在羅馬去世)
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.77,1:37:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}他同時也寫了很多書
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.86,1:37:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那些書都很好
